The Next War Could Be in Space

Check out all my sources for this video here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1uTVtYurIaszRpJ2Q5S0vgVnPUf4OHDWyIPjn1eRAqeo/edit?usp=drive_link

Militaries depend on satellites for communication, intelligence, and navigation. As the number of satellites grows, so has the number of attacks. There’s now attacks happening nearly every day. Here’s how nations are vying for power and what they’re now developing to take control.
